# üß† 1-Month MERN Full Stack Developer Learning Plan
 
This repository contains a comprehensive 1-month learning plan for MERN Full Stack Development, including AWS, Azure, cloud security best practices, weekday and weekend schedules, time management tools, and a suggested daily routine outside working hours.
 
