---
 
## üìÖ Weekly Breakdown
 
### Week 1: React.js + AWS S3 + Cloud Security
- Advanced React (Hooks, Context API, Redux Toolkit)
- Component optimization, routing, responsive UI
- Host frontend on AWS S3 + CloudFront
- Cloud security: IAM roles, HTTPS, logging
 
### Week 2: Node.js + Express + MongoDB + AWS EC2
- RESTful API, JWT auth, Mongoose schemas
- Deploy backend on EC2, MongoDB Atlas
- Cloud security: Security groups, Secrets Manager, CloudWatch
 
### Week 3: Full Stack Integration + Azure + CI/CD
- Frontend-backend integration, Docker, CI/CD
- Deploy full-stack app on Azure App Service
- Azure security: Key Vault, App Service Auth, Managed Identity
 
### Week 4: Advanced Features + Final Project + Security Review
- WebSockets, Redis caching, performance tuning
- Final MERN project with documentation
- Security audit: OWASP ZAP, Snyk, WAF, HTTPS
 
---
 
## ‚úÖ Time Management Tools
 
### Planning & Tracking
- **Notion**: Daily planner, resource links, progress tracking
- **Trello**: Weekly boards and task cards
- **Google Calendar**: Block study hours, set reminders
 
### Focus & Productivity
- **Pomofocus**: Pomodoro timer
- **Forest App**: Gamified focus tool
- **Todoist**: Task manager with priorities
 
### Progress Monitoring
- **Clockify**: Time tracking
- **Obsidian**: Structured note-taking
- **GitHub Projects**: Issue tracking and milestones
 
---
 
## üìÅ Repository Structure (Suggested)
- `/frontend`: React.js codebase
- `/backend`: Node.js + Express API
- `/docs`: Documentation and README files
- `/deploy`: Scripts and configs for AWS/Azure deployment
